02:03:07,680 --> 02:03:21,880
Pretty sympathetic to, which is this Silurian hypothesis. This idea of, uh, these aliens, what we're calling aliens, we're calling them extraterrestrials, but maybe they've been cohabiting with us on earth for a while.

