1825
02:04:49,940 --> 02:05:16,060
To have a healthy dose of yo, maybe yes, maybe no, because in all of our lives, we see things and assume things that just aren't true. And so, uh, in a sense, the book is about a character, but in a sense, it's about all of the readers too, because each reader is going to bring their own needs and wants their own obstacles. And we want to leave them with a gift.

